{"tid":161151,"cid":30,"subCid":0,"title":"你地冇資格怨厹，要怨就怨自己廢","createTime":"2017-03-18T10:36:39.000Z","updateTime":"2017-03-18T13:29:47.000Z","uid":64247,"like":0,"dislike":7,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"3951ce686ad5f1201b77047bda7689ca5d9a88dc","tid":161151,"uid":64247,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-18T10:36:39.000Z","msg":"見你班連登仔成日屌柒啲厹就覺得你地嘔心<br />\n<br />\n明明係自己冇料先比人乘虛而入<br />\n<br />\n比厹得米之後仲要話自己愛過嘅人係雞同公廁<br />\n<br />\n但有冇諗過係自己唔及人地？ <br />\n<br />\n冇夢想，冇目標，冇上進心，冇錢，乜柒都冇<br />\n<br />\n世界上咁多厹，你邊有得同人鬥？<br />\n<br />\n我係你地我就自動shut up，默默承受現實，唔再叫春，做返一個真男人，唔好再阻住人地開心咁生活<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wink.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n利申：紅巴"},{"pid":"f89e6e415258b3706cb6273bd92cde767b81a04d","tid":161151,"uid":64247,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-18T10:42:41.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wink.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"270d9fbb6f3e40c93dccc2558f69b1be6ea01ad3","tid":161151,"uid":64247,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-18T10:48:09.000Z","msg":"唔敢駁<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/oh.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"56111fa20ab1e94d1054c717d4adec2e74d02877","tid":161151,"uid":64247,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-18T10:56:59.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wink.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7ab02b344ce436c72c8c9dfe64161452113a45df","tid":161151,"uid":64247,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-18T11:14:01.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"de65b47981fb6576974f2fc7849fda2270dad921","tid":161151,"uid":64247,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-18T13:29:47.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}